Apache upload progress module. Works with mod_passenger (aka mod_rails).

It's still in development.
TODO:
  - add more messages to logs for debugging
  - abbility to define shared cache size (currently size is 10kB)

To install and activate module:
apxs2 -c -i -a mod_upload_progress.c

Config:
<Location />
    # enable tracking uploads in /
    TrackUploads On
</Location>

<Location /progress>
    # enable upload progress reports for /progress dir
    ReportUploads On
</Location>